column3: I have more string and translations updates, but don't want to bloat this pull, so it get's merged faster.\n@laanwj Can you take a look please?\n
@laanwj Same here, I have more to come for coin control, but would love to see this merged first...\n
@diapolo Code changes are OK, if you want to continue along these lines you could create a pull request that depends on this one \n(I did the same with #3332 and #3320)\n
@laanwj As it were mostly text and ui file changes I added a new commit to this pull instead.\n
